{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, ChatGPT can guide students in hypothesis formulation, experiment design, and data analysis, enhancing their understanding of scientific processes [8], and foster critical thinking skills through interaction and instant feedback [9], thus creating a more dynamic and effective learning environment for developing investigative competencies.The integration of emerging technologies in education has been a subject of study in recent decades [10].",
    "AI tools like ChatGPT can support various phases of the investigative process, from information search to document writing [11].",
    "However, literature on the specific impact of ChatGPT on the development of investigative competencies is still limited.",
    "This research fills that gap by providing a detailed evaluation of ChatGPT's functionality, contribution, and usability in the educational context.",
    "In the digital age, investigative competencies are essential for the academic and professional development of higher education students [12]."
  ]
}